Player vs player controls:
(to the left: player 1's controls, to the right: player 2's controls)
move_up: arrow_up / s
move_down: arrow_down / x
pause: b
use "super shot": i / q (cost: 1 bar)
shrink enemy: o / w (cost: 2 bars)
reverse ball's x_direction: p / e (cost: 3 bars)
Player vs bot controls: same as player 1's
Skin menu:
choose skin for player 1: mouse_left_button
choose skin for player 2: mouse_right_button
Warning: currently bot is designed to be unbeatable, so good luck :)
